[quote=“Ewa Hax, post:1, topic:114191”]Andy just click control panel … network server… support…get the ip address type it in the address bar of the internet.
Then click virtual servers and fill the data in. That will probally all you need.
Hope this was helpful XD

~ Ewa Hax ~[/quote]
